Firegento - Magento Module Composer Repository

Please visit https://github.com/magento-hackathon/composer-repository for further informaton.

Adding the repository to composer.json: 
{
    "repositories": [
        {
            "type": "composer",
            "url": "http://packages.firegento.com"
        }
    ]
}

connect20/at_addr

Every order in a storeowner's system has the potential to create a profit or loss. Many storeowners' profit margins are so thin that any additional costs associated with fulfillment will put you in the red. AccurateTax realizes how important accurate address data is not just for sales tax calculations, but also for shipping purposes. To this end, we have created the US Address Validation service from AccurateTax. Originally, the Address validation service was solely intended to determine what the zip+4 zipcodes were for sales tax calculation purposes; however, we quickly realized as we began using the service ourselves that this solution would likely decrease the costly address correction fees that many shippers charge when addresses have not been validated.

License OSL-v3.0
Authors Donald Organ
Releases 1.0

connect20/at_adv

AccurateTax Tax Tools - Advanced version provides the capability for shoppers to have accurate sales tax calculated for their orders based on the storeowner's nexus. The module makes at least two calls per order - the first is to verify the shipping address and determine the zip+4 zipcode, the second call is for accurately determining the sales tax rate based on the zip+4 zipcode.

License OSL-v3.0
Authors Donald Organ
Releases 1.1, 1.0

connect20/at_basic

AccurateTax Tax Tools - Basic version provides the capability for shoppers to have accurate sales tax calculated for their orders based on the storeowner's nexus. The system allows the shopper to enter either a 5-digit or zip+4 zipcode into their address information and will determine the correct sales tax rates based on that data.

License OSL-v3.0
Authors Donald Organ

spranks/configurable-tier-prices

This extension changes the way Magento calculates tier prices of configurable products. You can now add different variants of a configurable product to the cart and you will get the tier price for the total quantity of all variants in the cart.
